### Demo API Examples
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@studentId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@tutorId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@sessionId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Session Summary - Missing Transcript (Edge Case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/summaries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "{{sessionId}}",
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "tutor_id": "{{tutorId}}",
  "transcript": null,
  "session_duration_minutes": 30,
  "subject": "Algebra",
  "topics_covered": []
}

### 3. Session Summary - Mixed Subjects (Edge Case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/summaries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "{{sessionId}}",
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "tutor_id": "{{tutorId}}",
  "transcript": "Tutor: Let's start with factoring polynomials. Can you factor x² + 5x + 6? Student: That would be (x + 2)(x + 3). Tutor: Great! Now let's switch to chemistry. How do you balance H₂ + O₂ → H₂O? Student: 2H₂ + O₂ → 2H₂O",
  "session_duration_minutes": 45,
  "subject": "Math",
  "topics_covered": ["factoring", "chemical_equations"]
}

### 4. Practice Assignment - Bank Items Unavailable (Edge Case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/practice/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "subject": "Advanced Quantum Physics",
  "num_items": 5
}

### 5. Q&A - Ambiguous Query (Edge Case) ⭐ SHOWSTOPPER
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/qa/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "query": "I don't get this",
  "context": {
    "recent_sessions": ["Algebra", "Chemistry"],
    "current_practice": "quadratic equations"
  }
}

### 6. Q&A - Multi-Part Query (Edge Case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/qa/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "query": "Explain photosynthesis and also help me with factoring quadratics.",
  "context": {
    "subjects": ["Biology", "Algebra"]
  }
}

### 7. Q&A - Out-of-Scope Query (Edge Case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/qa/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "query": "What's the weather tomorrow?",
  "context": {}
}

